Police are investigating the case in which the famous scientist was attacked and robbed in his Gauteng home. JOHANNESBURG Famous numerologist Douglas Forbes s family says he is in hospital fighting for his life days after he was attacked and robbed at his Observatory home.Forbes s son Brad says his family is worried as his father constantly goes in and out of consciousness.Police are investigating the attack.Brad Forbes says they rushed the scientist to the hospital on Thursday but his kidneys failed at the emergency room and is currently in the Intensive Care Unit (ICU). After he was attacked, he was battling to move and I could see the one side of his face was all red. I managed to get him up we got him to emergency room and it was in the emergency room where his kidneys failed. They got him straight to ICU and at the moment he is fighting for his life.